item.description: 题目 Problem A Power Profile of a Cyclist Develop a model that can be applied to any type of rider that determines the relationship between the rider’s position on the course and the power the rider applies. Keep in mind that the rider has a limit on the total energy that can be expended over the course, as well as limits that accumulate
